1. Simple Program
	1.1 Character Set
		Letter: A~Z, a~z
		Digital: 0-9
		Special Character: ! # % ^ & * _ + = - ~ < > / \ ' " ; . , : ? ( ) [ ] { }

	1.2 Token
		1.2.1 Key Words
			asm auto bool break case catch char
			class const const_cast continue default delete do
			double dynamic_cast else enum explicit export extern
			false float for friend goto if inline
			itn long mutable namespace new operator private
			protected public register reinterpret_cast return short signed
			sizeof static static_cast struct switch template this
			throw true try typedef typeid typename union
			unsigned using virtual void volatile wcahr_t while

		1.2.2 Identifier
			Started with A-Z, a-z, _
			Consists of A-Z, a-z, _, 0-9
			Case sensitive
			Can't be keywords

		1.2.3 Word
			Number, Charactor, String, Boolean

		1.2.4 Operator
		
		1.2.5 Delimiter
			() {} , : ;

		1.2.6 Blank(kongbai)
			white(kongge), Tabsï¼Œ Vertical Tabs, line break, carriage return and annotation
		
			
